{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTag","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Indicators"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Appearances","level":2,"anchor":"Appearances"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags have two appearances so as to highlight or not their content:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"emphasized"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with a solid, high-contrast background. Used to draw strong attention to important","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"labels or categories. Emphasized tags stand out prominently against the interface and are ideal for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"primary or high-priority information.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"muted","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a subtle, light, or semi-transparent background. Used for secondary or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"less prominent information. Muted tags blend more with the background, providing a softer visual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"emphasis compared to emphasized tags.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Status","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Status"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags have seven status depending on the context of the information they represent. Each state is designed","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to convey a specific meaning and ensure clarity in communication.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Neutral"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Default or inactive state. Used for standard labels, categories, or when no specific","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"status needs to be communicated.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Accent"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Used to draw attention to new features, recommendations, or content suggestions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Invites users to explore and engage with new offerings, creating an exciting and engaging experience.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Positive"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Indicates success, confirmation, or a positive status. Commonly used to highlight","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"completed actions or approved items."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Warning","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Signals caution or a potentially risky situation. Used to draw attention to items"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"requiring user awareness or intervention."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Negative"}]},{"text":": Represents errors, critical issues, or urgent attention needed. Used to highlight","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"problems or failed actions.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Info","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Conveys informational messages or supplementary details. Used for neutral, helpful,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or contextual information.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Disabled","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Shows that the tag is inactive and cannot be interacted with. Appears faded or greyed out. This is not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"allowed when loader is activated.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Shape","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Shape"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags can have two shapes:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Rounded","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with fully rounded corners, creating a pill-shaped appearance. Rounded","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tags offer a softer and more approachable look, suitable for most modern interfaces.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Square","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with sharp, square corners. Squared tags provide a more formal, structured, or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"technical feel. They are often used in business contexts to label promotions, offers, or important notices.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Size","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Size"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags can have two sizes:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Default","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": The standard tag size, suitable for most use cases and offering good readability.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Small","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A compact tag with reduced height and font size. Used when saving space is important or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when grouping elements visually.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Layout","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Layout"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"There are four available layouts for tags:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"-","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text only","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that displays only text. Used for simple labels, categories, or keywords without additional visual"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"elements.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Bullet"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with a small indicator (dot) alongside the text. Used to show status, presence, or activity","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"next to the label."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Icon"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that includes an icon before the text. Used to visually reinforce the meaning of the tag,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as status, type, or action.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Loader"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag that combines a loading spinner (or progress indicator) with text. Used to indicate that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a process or action related to the tag is in progress.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Code samples"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Text only with neutral status, for emphasized appearance with rounded shape in default size","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\",  status: .neutral(), appearance: .emphasized, shape: .rounded, size: .default)","    \/\/ Or also","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\")","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(leading: .bullet)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with a custom decorative icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")))","    \/\/ If your layout is in RTL mode but your tag has an icon with another meaning because of bad orientation,","    \/\/ you can flip the icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"), flipIcon: true))","","    \/\/ Text with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(bullet: true))","","    \/\/ Tag with loader with rounded shape in small size","    OUDSTag(loadingLabel: \"Label\", shape: .rounded, size: .small)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Design documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-tag","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Themes rendering"},{"anchor":"Orange","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_Orange","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange Business Tools"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_OrangeBusinessTools","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Sosh","anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Wireframe","text":"Wireframe","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_tag_Wireframe","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Version","style":"note","type":"aside"},{"style":"note","name":"Since","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.18.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstag"]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A tag is a small element that shows short information like a label, keyword, or category."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It helps users quickly find, group, or understand content.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"]}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Structures","title":"Structures","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Status"]},{"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(label:status:appearance:shape:size:hasLoader:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(loadingLabel:shape:size:)"]},{"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/body"]},{"anchor":"Enumerations","title":"Enumerations","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Appearance","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Shape","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Size"]},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponent